      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it is very solid, with a smooth-shifting transmission and an engine that runs quietly and reliably. The exterior is clean with a nice shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is tidy and free of any major wear or odors, making for a very comfortable driving experience. It\u2019s a great choice for someone looking for a dependable, attractive car that is ready for the road.",
