    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit features crisp throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies and delivers power through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Key preventive maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The limited-slip differential provides predictable lock-up, and the suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain is robust, pulling hard to the 8,000 RPM redline with the signature metallic rasp. A driver-focused example with all major mechanical hurdles cleared.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
